UPDATE map_visualization
            SET dataset = $1,
                map_type = $2,
                subcategory = $3,
                name = $4,
                legend_ticks = $5,
                color_palette = $6,
                reverse_scale = $7,
                invert_normalized = $8,
                scale_type = $9,
                show_pdf = $10,
                default_start_date = $11,
                default_end_date = $12,
                default_source = $13,
                formatter_type = $14,
                legend_formatter_type = $15,
                decimals = $16,
                legend_decimals = $17
            WHERE id = $18
